00:31:51,742 --> 00:31:53,077
Jalan terus!

455
00:31:53,619 --> 00:31:54,912
Lebih cepat!

456
00:31:55,997 --> 00:31:57,248
Apa yang kau lakukan?

457
00:31:57,832 --> 00:31:59,917
- Lebih cepat!
- Jalan!

458
00:32:01,669 --> 00:32:04,046
- Mubaek!
- Mubaek!

459
00:32:04,755 --> 00:32:07,008
- Mubaek!
- Mubaek!

460
00:32:11,470 --> 00:32:14,182
Mubaek, apa-apaan ini?

461
00:32:14,265 --> 00:32:15,725
Di mana Tagon?

462
00:32:16,225 --> 00:32:17,560
Jalan!

463
00:32:18,895 --> 00:32:20,354
Lebih cepat!

464
00:32:23,107 --> 00:32:24,233
Lebih cepat!

465
00:33:02,313 --> 00:33:03,689
- Tagon.
- Tagon.

466
00:33:05,775 --> 00:33:07,360
Terima kasih sudah datang.

467
00:33:07,443 --> 00:33:09,111
Bagaimana kau bisa terpikir ide ini?

468
00:33:14,408 --> 00:33:15,409
Iark.

469
00:34:45,166 --> 00:34:47,293
Aku tak bisa dengar suara spirit.

470
00:34:49,378 --> 00:34:52,340
Aku tak hafal tarian memanggil spirit
seperti Ibu.

471
00:34:54,592 --> 00:34:56,844
Aku bahkan belum bisa bermimpi.

472
00:35:01,265 --> 00:35:03,893
Kenapa aku tak bisa kabur bersama Eunseom?

473
00:35:06,228 --> 00:35:07,605
Karena kau terikat.

474
00:35:12,151 --> 00:35:13,277
Benarkah?

475
00:35:14,195 --> 00:35:17,239
Aku terikat pada apa?

476
00:35:19,450 --> 00:35:20,493
Namamu.

477
00:35:21,786 --> 00:35:23,454
Namamu, Tanya.

478
00:35:24,372 --> 00:35:26,332
Sebagai anggota Suku Wahan.

479
00:35:27,541 --> 00:35:29,794
Fakta bahwa kau putri Yeolson,

480
00:35:30,878 --> 00:35:33,172
kepala suku berikutnya,

481
00:35:34,423 --> 00:35:37,593
dan anak dari ramalan tentang Komet Biru.

482
